        [Distinct1].[C5] AS [C5], 
        [Distinct1].[C6] AS [C6], 
        [Distinct1].[C7] AS [C7], 
        [Distinct1].[C8] AS [C8]
        FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
            [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
            [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
            [UnionAll1].[role_name] AS [C3], 
            [UnionAll1].[role_id] AS [C4],

                [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name],

                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[uvr_role_id] = [Extent3].[role_id]

                [Extent7].[role_id] AS [role_id],

                [Extent5].[user_phone] AS [user_phone],

                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[uvr_role_id] = [Extent3].[role_id]

    [Project4].[C8] AS [C8]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Distinct1].[C1] AS [C1], 
        [Distinct1].[C2] AS [C2], 
        [Distinct1].[C3] AS [C3], 
        [Distinct1].[C4] AS [C4], 
        [Distinct1].[C5] AS [C5], 
        [Distinct1].[C6] AS [C6], 
        [Distinct1].[C7] AS [C7], 
        [Distinct1].[C8] AS [C8]
        FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
            [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
            [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
            [UnionAll1].[role_name] AS [C3], 
            [UnionAll1].[role_id] AS [C4], 
            [UnionAll1].[user_name] AS [C5],

                1 AS [C1],

                [Extent3].[role_id] AS [role_id], 
                [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name],

                [Extent1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]
                FROM    [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvr_user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[uvr_role_id] = [Extent3].[role_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent4].[uvs_user_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent2].[uvr_role_id] > 2) AND ([Extent4].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
            UNION ALL
                SELECT 
                1 AS [C1], 
                [Extent5].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
                [Extent7].[role_name] AS [role_name], 
                [Extent7].[role_id] AS [role_id], 
                [Extent5].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
                [Extent5].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path],

                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_Roles] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent6].[uvr_role_id] = [Extent7].[role_id]

SELECT 
    [Project4].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project4].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Project4].[C3] AS [C3], 
    [Project4].[C4] AS [C4], 
    [Project4].[C5] AS [C5], 
    [Project4].[C6] AS [C6], 
    [Project4].[C7] AS [C7], 
    [Project4].[C8] AS [C8]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Distinct1].[C1] AS [C1], 
        [Distinct1].[C2] AS [C2], 
        [Distinct1].[C3] AS [C3], 
        [Distinct1].[C4] AS [C4], 
        [Distinct1].[C5] AS [C5], 
        [Distinct1].[C6] AS [C6], 
        [Distinct1].[C7] AS [C7], 
        [Distinct1].[C8] AS [C8]
        FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
            [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
            [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
            [UnionAll1].[role_name] AS [C3], 
            [UnionAll1].[role_id] AS [C4], 
            [UnionAll1].[user_name] AS [C5], 
            [UnionAll1].[user_phone] AS [C6], 
            [UnionAll1].[user_photo_path] AS [C7], 
            [UnionAll1].[user_login_times] AS [C8]
            FROM  (SELECT 
                1 AS [C1], 
                [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
                [Extent3].[role_name] AS [role_name], 
                [Extent3].[role_id] AS [role_id], 
                [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
                [Extent1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
                [Extent1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]
                FROM    [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvr_user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[uvr_role_id] = [Extent3].[role_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent4].[uvs_user_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent2].[uvr_role_id] > 2) AND ([Extent4].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
            UNION ALL
                SELECT 
                1 AS [C1], 
                [Extent5].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
                [Extent7].[role_name] AS [role_name], 
                [Extent7].[role_id] AS [role_id], 
                [Extent5].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
                [Extent5].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
                [Extent5].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]
                FROM    [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent5]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[user_id] = [Extent6].[uvr_user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_Roles] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent6].[uvr_role_id] = [Extent7].[role_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent5].[user_id] = [Extent8].[uvs_user_id]
                WHERE ([Extent5].[user_id] = @p__linq__1) OR (([Extent6].[uvr_role_id] > 2) AND ([Extent8].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))) AS [UnionAll1]
        )  AS [Distinct1]
    )  AS [Project4]
    ORDER BY [Project4].[C4] ASC, [Project4].[C5] ASC

SELECT 
    [GroupBy1].[A1] AS [C1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        COUNT(1) AS [A1]
        FROM        [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent2].[room_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[room_school_id] = [Extent3].[sys_school_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Course_Type] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_type_id] = [Extent4].[ct_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = [Extent5].[user_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent6].[user_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent7].[c_season_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent8].[sub_id]
        WHERE ([Extent2].[room_school_id] = (CASE WHEN (0 = @p__linq__0) THEN [Extent2].[room_school_id] ELSE @p__linq__1 END)) OR (([Extent2].[room_school_id] IS NULL) AND (CASE WHEN (0 = @p__linq__0) THEN [Extent2].[room_school_id] ELSE @p__linq__1 END IS NULL))
    )  AS [GroupBy1]
-- p__linq__0: '0' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: '0' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 10:19:02 +08:00
-- Completed in 10 ms with result: SqlDataReader

Opened connection at 2017/11/9 10:19:02 +08:00

    [Project1].[user_name1] AS [user_name], 
    [Project1].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], 
    [Project1].[course_introduce] AS [course_introduce], 
    [Project1].[course_max_num] AS [course_max_num], 
    [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project1].[c_room] AS [c_room], 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[c_cs_id] AS [c_cs_id], 
    [Project1].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
    [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
    [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project1].[c_teacher_id] AS [c_teacher_id], 
    [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name1], 
    [Project1].[c_type_id] AS [c_type_id], 
    [Project1].[ct_name] AS [ct_name], 
    [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info]
    FROM ( SELECT [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], [Project1].[course_introduce] AS [course_introduce], [Project1].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], [Project1].[course_max_num] AS [course_max_num], [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], [Project1].[c_type_id] AS [c_type_id], [Project1].[c_teacher_id] AS [c_teacher_id], [Project1].[c_room] AS [c_room], [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], [Project1].[c_cs_id] AS [c_cs_id], [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], [Project1].[ct_name] AS [ct_name], [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], [Project1].[user_name1] AS [user_name1], [Project1].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[c_cs_id] ASC, [Project1].[c_sub_id] ASC, [Project1].[course_name] ASC) AS [row_number]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Extent1].[course_introduce] AS [course_introduce], 
            [Extent1].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], 
            [Extent1].[course_max_num] AS [course_max_num],

            [Extent4].[ct_name] AS [ct_name], 
            [Extent5].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Extent6].[user_name] AS [user_name1], 
            [Extent7].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
            [Extent8].[sub_name] AS [sub_name]
            FROM        [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent2].[room_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[room_school_id] = [Extent3].[sys_school_id]

            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent8].[sub_id]

        )  AS [Project1]
    )  AS [Project1]
    WHERE [Project1].[row_number] > 0
    ORDER BY [Project1].[c_cs_id] ASC, [Project1].[c_sub_id] ASC, [Project1].[course_name] ASC

SELECT 
    [GroupBy1].[A1] AS [C1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        COUNT(1) AS [A1]
        FROM        [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent2].[room_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[room_school_id] = [Extent3].[sys_school_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Course_Type] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_type_id] = [Extent4].[ct_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = [Extent5].[user_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent6].[user_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent7].[c_season_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent8].[sub_id]
        WHERE (([Extent2].[room_school_id] = (CASE WHEN (0 = @p__linq__0) THEN [Extent2].[room_school_id] ELSE @p__linq__1 END)) OR (([Extent2].[room_school_id] IS NULL) AND (CASE WHEN (0 = @p__linq__0) THEN [Extent2].[room_school_id] ELSE @p__linq__1 END IS NULL))) AND ([Extent1].[c_cs_id] = @p__linq__2) AND ([Extent1].[c_sub_id] = @p__linq__3)
    )  AS [GroupBy1]

        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Extent1].[course_introduce] AS [course_introduce], 
            [Extent1].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], 
            [Extent1].[course_max_num] AS [course_max_num],

            CASE WHEN (0 = [Extent2].[room_id]) THEN N'' ELSE CASE WHEN ([Extent3].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent3].[sys_school_name] END + CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent2].[room_name] END END AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[ct_name] AS [ct_name], 
            [Extent5].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Extent6].[user_name] AS [user_name1], 
            [Extent7].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
            [Extent8].[sub_name] AS [sub_name]
            FROM        [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent2].[room_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[room_school_id] = [Extent3].[sys_school_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Course_Type] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_type_id] = [Extent4].[ct_id]

            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent8].[sub_id]

        )  AS [Project1]
    )  AS [Project1]
    WHERE [Project1].[row_number] > 0
    ORDER BY [Project1].[c_cs_id] ASC, [Project1].[c_sub_id] ASC, [Project1].[course_name] ASC

SELECT 
    [GroupBy1].[A1] AS [C1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        COUNT(1) AS [A1]
        FROM        [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent2].[room_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[room_school_id] = [Extent3].[sys_school_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Course_Type] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_type_id] = [Extent4].[ct_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = [Extent5].[user_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent6].[user_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent7].[c_season_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent8].[sub_id]
        WHERE ([Extent2].[room_school_id] = (CASE WHEN (0 = @p__linq__0) THEN [Extent2].[room_school_id] ELSE @p__linq__1 END)) OR (([Extent2].[room_school_id] IS NULL) AND (CASE WHEN (0 = @p__linq__0) THEN [Extent2].[room_school_id] ELSE @p__linq__1 END IS NULL))
    )  AS [GroupBy1]
-- p__linq__0: '0' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: '0' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 10:26:21 +08:00
-- Completed in 4 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT TOP (10) 
    [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project1].[user_name1] AS [user_name], 
    [Project1].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], 
    [Project1].[course_introduce] AS [course_introduce], 
    [Project1].[course_max_num] AS [course_max_num], 
    [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project1].[c_room] AS [c_room], 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[c_cs_id] AS [c_cs_id], 
    [Project1].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
    [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
    [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project1].[c_teacher_id] AS [c_teacher_id], 
    [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name1], 
    [Project1].[c_type_id] AS [c_type_id], 
    [Project1].[ct_name] AS [ct_name], 
    [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info]
    FROM ( SELECT [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], [Project1].[course_introduce] AS [course_introduce], [Project1].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], [Project1].[course_max_num] AS [course_max_num], [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], [Project1].[c_type_id] AS [c_type_id], [Project1].[c_teacher_id] AS [c_teacher_id], [Project1].[c_room] AS [c_room], [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], [Project1].[c_cs_id] AS [c_cs_id], [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], [Project1].[ct_name] AS [ct_name], [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], [Project1].[user_name1] AS [user_name1], [Project1].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[c_cs_id] ASC, [Project1].[c_sub_id] ASC, [Project1].[course_name] ASC) AS [row_number]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Extent1].[course_introduce] AS [course_introduce], 
            [Extent1].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], 
            [Extent1].[course_max_num] AS [course_max_num], 
            [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Extent1].[c_type_id] AS [c_type_id], 
            [Extent1].[c_teacher_id] AS [c_teacher_id], 
            [Extent1].[c_room] AS [c_room], 
            [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Extent1].[c_cs_id] AS [c_cs_id], 
            CASE WHEN (0 = [Extent2].[room_id]) THEN N'' ELSE CASE WHEN ([Extent3].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent3].[sys_school_name] END + CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent2].[room_name] END END AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[ct_name] AS [ct_name], 
            [Extent5].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Extent6].[user_name] AS [user_name1], 
            [Extent7].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
            [Extent8].[sub_name] AS [sub_name]
            FROM        [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent2].[room_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[room_school_id] = [Extent3].[sys_school_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Course_Type] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_type_id] = [Extent4].[ct_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = [Extent5].[user_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent6].[user_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent7].[c_season_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent8].[sub_id]
            WHERE ([Extent2].[room_school_id] = (CASE WHEN (0 = @p__linq__0) THEN [Extent2].[room_school_id] ELSE @p__linq__1 END)) OR (([Extent2].[room_school_id] IS NULL) AND (CASE WHEN (0 = @p__linq__0) THEN [Extent2].[room_school_id] ELSE @p__linq__1 END IS NULL))
        )  AS [Project1]
    )  AS [Project1]
    WHERE [Project1].[row_number] > 0
    ORDER BY [Project1].[c_cs_id] ASC, [Project1].[c_sub_id] ASC, [Project1].[course_name] ASC

            [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Extent1].[course_introduce] AS [course_introduce],

            CASE WHEN (0 = [Extent2].[room_id]) THEN N'' ELSE CASE WHEN ([Extent3].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent3].[sys_school_name] END + CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent2].[room_name] END END AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[ct_name] AS [ct_name], 
            [Extent5].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Extent6].[user_name] AS [user_name1], 
            [Extent7].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
            [Extent8].[sub_name] AS [sub_name]

            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent2].[room_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[room_school_id] = [Extent3].[sys_school_id]

            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent7].[c_season_id]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent8].[sub_id]

        )  AS [Project1]
    )  AS [Project1]
    WHERE [Project1].[row_number] > 0

SELECT 
    [Distinct1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Distinct1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Distinct1].[C3] AS [C3]
    FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
        [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_name] AS [C3]
        FROM  (SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent3].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent3].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__1) AND ([Extent2].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
        UNION ALL
            SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent4].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent4]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent5].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent6].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent4].[user_id] = @p__linq__2) OR (([Extent6].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__3) AND ([Extent5].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))) AS [UnionAll1]
    )  AS [Distinct1]

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 10:43:44 +08:00
-- Completed in 11 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 10:43:52 +08:00
-- Completed in 0 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)

-- Completed in 12 ms with result: SqlDataReader

    [GroupBy1].[A1] AS [C1]
    FROM ( SELECT

SELECT 
    [Distinct1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Distinct1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Distinct1].[C3] AS [C3]
    FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
        [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_name] AS [C3]
        FROM  (SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent3].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent3].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__1) AND ([Extent2].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
        UNION ALL
            SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent4].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent4]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent5].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent6].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent4].[user_id] = @p__linq__2) OR (([Extent6].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__3) AND ([Extent5].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))) AS [UnionAll1]
    )  AS [Distinct1]

-- p__linq__2: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__3: '2' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 10:46:03 +08:00
-- Completed in 15 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 10:47:11 +08:00
-- Completed in 0 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Distinct1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Distinct1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Distinct1].[C3] AS [C3]
    FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
        [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_name] AS [C3]
        FROM  (SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent3].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent3].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__1) AND ([Extent2].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
        UNION ALL
            SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent4].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent4]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent5].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent6].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent4].[user_id] = @p__linq__2) OR (([Extent6].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__3) AND ([Extent5].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))) AS [UnionAll1]
    )  AS [Distinct1]
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: '2' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__2: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__3: '2' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 11:39:33 +08:00
-- Completed in 6 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

SELECT 
    [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Extent2].[cvt_time] AS [cvt_time]
    FROM    [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
    INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_vs_Time] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[course_id] = [Extent2].[cvt_course_id]
    LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[cvt_room_id] = [Extent3].[room_id]
    LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_School] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[room_school_id] = [Extent4].[school_id]
    WHERE [Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0 OR [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = @p__linq__1

    [Limit1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
    [Limit1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Limit1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
    [Limit1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
    [Limit1].[user_info] AS [user_info], 
    [Limit1].[user_email] AS [user_email], 
    [Limit1].[user_password] AS [user_password], 
    [Limit1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
    [Limit1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address], 
    [Limit1].[user_work_unit] AS [user_work_unit], 
    [Limit1].[user_add_time] AS [user_add_time], 
    [Limit1].[user_add_user] AS [user_add_user], 
    [Limit1].[user_update_time] AS [user_update_time], 
    [Limit1].[user_update_user] AS [user_update_user], 
    [Limit1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times], 
    [Limit1].[user_state] AS [user_state]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
        [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Extent1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
        [Extent1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
        [Extent1].[user_info] AS [user_info], 
        [Extent1].[user_email] AS [user_email], 
        [Extent1].[user_password] AS [user_password], 
        [Extent1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
        [Extent1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address], 
        [Extent1].[user_work_unit] AS [user_work_unit], 
        [Extent1].[user_add_time] AS [user_add_time], 
        [Extent1].[user_add_user] AS [user_add_user], 
        [Extent1].[user_update_time] AS [user_update_time], 
        [Extent1].[user_update_user] AS [user_update_user], 
        [Extent1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times], 
        [Extent1].[user_state] AS [user_state]

    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1],

        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model],

SELECT 
    [Distinct1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Distinct1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Distinct1].[C3] AS [C3]
    FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
        [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_name] AS [C3]
        FROM  (SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent3].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent3].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__1) AND ([Extent2].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
        UNION ALL
            SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent4].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent4]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent5].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent6].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent4].[user_id] = @p__linq__2) OR (([Extent6].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__3) AND ([Extent5].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))) AS [UnionAll1]
    )  AS [Distinct1]
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: '2' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__2: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__3: '2' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 14:35:53 +08:00
-- Completed in 20 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)

    [Limit1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
    [Limit1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address], 
    [Limit1].[user_work_unit] AS [user_work_unit],

    [Filter1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Filter1].[cvt_id] AS [cvt_id], 
    [Filter1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Filter1].[cvt_time] AS [cvt_time]
    FROM   (SELECT [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], [Extent1].[c_teacher_id] AS [c_teacher_id], [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] AS [c_assistant_id], [Extent2].[cvt_id] AS [cvt_id], [Extent2].[cvt_time] AS [cvt_time], [Extent2].[cvt_duration] AS [cvt_duration], [Extent3].[room_school_id] AS [room_school_id]
        FROM   [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_vs_Time] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[course_id] = [Extent2].[cvt_course_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[cvt_room_id] = [Extent3].[room_id]
        WHERE 0 = (DATEDIFF (day, SysDateTime(), [Extent2].[cvt_time])) ) AS [Filter1]

SELECT 
    [Filter1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Filter1].[cvt_id] AS [cvt_id], 
    [Filter1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Filter1].[cvt_time] AS [cvt_time]
    FROM   (SELECT [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], [Extent1].[c_teacher_id] AS [c_teacher_id], [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] AS [c_assistant_id], [Extent2].[cvt_id] AS [cvt_id], [Extent2].[cvt_time] AS [cvt_time], [Extent2].[cvt_duration] AS [cvt_duration], [Extent3].[room_school_id] AS [room_school_id]
        FROM   [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_vs_Time] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[course_id] = [Extent2].[cvt_course_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[cvt_room_id] = [Extent3].[room_id]
        WHERE 0 = (DATEDIFF (day, SysDateTime(), [Extent2].[cvt_time])) ) AS [Filter1]
    LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_School] AS [Extent4] ON [Filter1].[room_school_id] = [Extent4].[school_id]
    WHERE ([Filter1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0 OR [Filter1].[c_assistant_id] = @p__linq__1) AND (([Filter1].[cvt_time] >= @p__linq__2) OR ((DATEADD (minute, [Filter1].[cvt_duration], [Filter1].[cvt_time])) > (SysDateTime())))

            WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent3].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__1) AND ([Extent2].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
        UNION ALL

            [Extent4].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent4].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent4]

    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1],

    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model],

SELECT TOP (1) 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0

    )  AS [GroupBy1]

SELECT TOP (1) 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[MigrationId] DESC

        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[cvt_room_id] = [Extent3].[room_id]
        WHERE 0 = (DATEDIFF (day, SysDateTime(), [Extent2].[cvt_time])) ) AS [Filter1]

SELECT 
    [Distinct1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Distinct1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Distinct1].[C3] AS [C3]
    FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
        [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_name] AS [C3]
        FROM  (SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent3].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent3].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__1) AND ([Extent2].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
        UNION ALL
            SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent4].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent4]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent5].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent6].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent4].[user_id] = @p__linq__2) OR (([Extent6].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__3) AND ([Extent5].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))) AS [UnionAll1]
    )  AS [Distinct1]

-- p__linq__1: '2' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)

    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)

SELECT 
    [Distinct1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Distinct1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Distinct1].[C3] AS [C3]
    FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT 
        [UnionAll1].[C1] AS [C1], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_id] AS [C2], 
        [UnionAll1].[user_name] AS [C3]
        FROM  (SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent3].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent1].[user_id] = @p__linq__0) OR (([Extent3].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__1) AND ([Extent2].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))
        UNION ALL
            SELECT 
            1 AS [C1], 
            [Extent4].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
            [Extent4].[user_name] AS [user_name]
            FROM   [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent4]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Subject] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent5].[uvs_user_id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent4].[user_id] = [Extent6].[uvr_user_id]
            WHERE ([Extent4].[user_id] = @p__linq__2) OR (([Extent6].[uvr_role_id] > @p__linq__3) AND ([Extent5].[uvs_sub_id] IN (2, 3)))) AS [UnionAll1]
    )  AS [Distinct1]
-- p__linq__0: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: '2' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__2: '3' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__3: '2' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- Executing at 2017/11/9 15:48:36 +08:00
-- Completed in 6 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
